{"tid":145874,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"話說我係twitter比日本人呃左700幾蚊","createTime":"2017-03-06T14:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T15:36:10.000Z","uid":45055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ab172a2a10684f8b2bdbe77f676f0e170170196d","tid":145874,"uid":45055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T14:53:08.000Z","msg":"是咁的，有次上twitter同個日本人買野<br />\n雖然佢個acc係買賣專用而唔係正身<br />\n但又一直有活動同同人交易<br />\n咁我就同佢買左700蚊野，叫佢寄去個日本地址到，過完數佢就話聽日寄，會影張相比我睇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁因為買既野太多我都唔記得左，到左10日之後即係琴日先記得佢仲未寄比我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />於是我就direct mesaage左佢幾次，佢連睇都冇睇<br />\n但就繼續retweet其他人d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我個700蚊係咪凍過水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lnafkzxv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flnafkzxv&h=98646ce7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"490a0a140660b39459c39bf8a27bae8cb7ad60a3","tid":145874,"uid":21585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T14:58:10.000Z","msg":"你好似都唔係好care 咁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba8f8774820b4bda267d1e6d7b0d9bb604759008","tid":145874,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T14:59:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xx1A52p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxx1A52p.png&h=abe532a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e00a5d1101bd8050bfe660f0fdacd7dbc5781af","tid":145874,"uid":45055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T15:02:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你好似都唔係好care 咁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我買左成堆野以為人人都發左貨<br />\ncheck漏左姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/n